Chapter 14: The 180-Day Institution Plan
Core Question
What must happen over the next six months to make this durable?
Understand
The Institution Container should be built over time.
Do not try to formalize everything in one meeting.
Use the next 180 days to strengthen the society in phases.
The goal is durability.
