Chapter 15: Institution Report
Core Question
What can now outlive us?
Understand
The Institution Report asks what has become durable.
Not what was exciting.
Not what attracted attention.
Not what sounded good.
What can now outlive the original builders?
The report should show what has been documented, standardized, trained, rotated, protected, formalized, and evaluated.
